full_text:
Stars
Stars are celestial objects that create energy and emit light via nuclear fusion. 
Ingame, stars act as light sources in each star system. A system can have up to three stars, and each star can be one of a variety of colors.
Like planets and moons, stars are not interactable objects, and if you are able to get close enough to one, you will pass through with no effect.
